---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Operator — Christopher Campbell — SecureProspective">
  <Nav />

  <main>
    {/* ───────────────────────── PAGE HERO ───────────────────────── */}
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <div class="eyebrow">The Operator</div>
          <h1 class="page-title">
            <span class="reveal-word">Christopher</span>
            <span class="reveal-word">Campbell</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-sub">
            Business must adapt or suffer the inevitable. I built SecureProspective to make
            the adaptation deliberate.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* CSS-drawn portrait placeholder */}
        <div class="portrait" aria-hidden="true">
          <span>PORTRAIT</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* ───────────────────── THREE CAREERS ───────────────────── */}
    <section class="careers">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-label animate-in">Three careers. One spine.</div>

        <div class="careers-grid animate-group">
          <div class="career animate-item">
            <div class="career-name">Technology</div>
            <div class="career-role career-role--gold">The Passion</div>
            <p class="career-body">
              It taught me to look forward — to see the future state before it arrives and
              build toward it. Started at MCI WorldCom in 1999, age 19. Field deployments
              for Bank of America, USDA wide-area network, Cisco infrastructure. Twenty-six
              years in technology. This is the Transform movement of the method: not
              AI-powered, but AI-native. Prefix dropped.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="career animate-item">
            <div class="career-name">Construction</div>
            <div class="career-role career-role--gold">The Objective Truth</div>
            <p class="career-body">
              Fifteen years of electrical work. Commercial, residential, military bases.
              Low-voltage. Fire-alarm systems. Voltage is or is not present. Code is right
              or wrong. There is no spin in electrical work — only what is safe and what
              kills. This taught me Diagnose: find what is actually broken before touching
              anything. Most consulting de-emphasizes this step. I emphasize it.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="career animate-item">
            <div class="career-name">Insurance</div>
            <div class="career-role career-role--gold">The Responsibility</div>
            <p class="career-body">
              Life, annuity, running an IMO. Stewardship for clients' long-term outcomes.
              ~$110M in annuity production assisted over six years. ~$18M/yr current volume.
              Eight active agents. Licensed: TX Life/Health/Annuity 3096607. Federal benefits
              specialist: FERS, CSRS, TSP, FEHB, LEO/ATC/researcher variations. This taught
              me Position and Shape: set up systems that last, structure every output so the
              person who owns it can actually own it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* ───────────────────── METHOD ORIGIN ───────────────────── */}
    <section class="origin">
      <div class="container origin-inner animate-in">
        <p class="origin-quote">
          The four-movement method was not invented in a consulting deck.
        </p>
        <p class="origin-sub">
          It was distilled from three careers that each taught one part of it. One movement
          per career. Thirty years of evidence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* ───────────────────── PROOF ───────────────────── */}
    <section class="proof">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="block-title animate-in">Proof</h2>

        <div class="proof-grid animate-group">
          <a class="proof-item animate-item" href="/the-work#tfm">
            <div class="proof-label">TFM</div>
            <p class="proof-desc">
              Tech Freedom Ministries is the first external client. Full Astro site, brand
              system, digital infrastructure. Method applied end to end.
            </p>
            <span class="proof-link">View record 001 &rarr;</span>
          </a>
          <a class="proof-item animate-item" href="/the-work#imo-distilled">
            <div class="proof-label">The IMO</div>
            <p class="proof-desc">
              The second proof is internal. We ran one. We knew what was broken. We applied
              the method to our own business first.
            </p>
            <span class="proof-link">View record 002 &rarr;</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <a href="/the-work" class="btn animate-in">See the full work &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* ───────────────────── FAITH NOTE ───────────────────── */}
    <section class="faith-note">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="faith-text animate-in">
          Faith is part of who I am. It is why TFM exists as a client. SecureProspective is
          the consulting practice — built for businesses of any kind, faith-aligned or not.
          The method works the same either way.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* ───────────────────── CHATBOT TEASER ───────────────────── */}
    <section class="chatbot">
      <div class="container chatbot-inner animate-in">
        <h3 class="chatbot-title">Want the full background?</h3>
        <p class="chatbot-body">
          A chatbot is coming — hosted directly on this site, grounded in the full career
          record. It will answer anything you would ask of a resume: dates, metrics,
          specifics. Interrogation-proof depth on demand.
        </p>
        <span class="badge">Coming Soon</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* ───────────────────── CTA ───────────────────── */}
    <section class="cta">
      <div class="container cta-inner animate-in">
        <p class="cta-line">Ready to work together?</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn">Get in touch &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: var(--silver-base);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
    padding: var(--space-7) 0;
  }
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .hero-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .page-title {
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    line-height: 1.05;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-body-lg);
    max-width: 640px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── Portrait placeholder ── */
  .portrait {
    width: 220px;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    background: var(--ink);
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .portrait span {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--ink-inverted);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* ── Three careers ── */
  .careers {
    background: var(--white);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
    padding: var(--space-7) 0;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .careers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }
  .career {
    border-top: 2px solid var(--ink);
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
  }
  .career-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .career-role {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .career-role--gold {
    color: var(--gold-identity);
  }
  .career-body {
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ── Method origin ── */
  .origin {
    background: var(--blue-brand);
    color: var(--ink-inverted);
    padding: var(--space-6) 0;
  }
  .origin-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .origin-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
    max-width: 900px;
  }
  .origin-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-body-lg);
    color: var(--white);
    opacity: 0.85;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  /* ── Proof ── */
  .proof {
    background: var(--silver-base);
    padding: var(--space-7) 0;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .block-title {
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .proof-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .proof-item {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    padding: var(--space-5);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    transition: border-color 120ms ease-out;
  }
  .proof-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--blue-brand);
  }
  .proof-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .proof-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .proof-link {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--blue-brand);
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
  }

  /* ── Faith note ── */
  .faith-note {
    background: var(--white);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    padding: var(--space-5) 0;
  }
  .faith-text {
    font-size: var(--text-caption);
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0.7;
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  /* ── Chatbot teaser ── */
  .chatbot {
    background: var(--silver-base);
    padding: var(--space-6) 0;
  }
  .chatbot-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .chatbot-title {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
  }
  .chatbot-body {
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    max-width: 700px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  .badge {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    background: var(--yellow-accent);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 4px 12px;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .cta {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--ink-inverted);
    padding: var(--space-6) 0;
  }
  .cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cta-line {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .careers-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .page-title {
      font-size: var(--text-h2);
    }
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .portrait {
      width: 160px;
    }
    .origin-quote {
      font-size: var(--text-h3);
    }
    .proof-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
